  <def>BUDDH: the Buddha-land of Permanence, Tranquility, and Light (the Pure Land (淨土) where the dharma-bodies (法身) of all Buddhas reside (in the Tiāntái School one of the four regions, 四土); the region is referred to as 'permanent' 常 since there is no birth, death, nor any form of change; 'tranquil' because all delusions and afflictions have vanished, 'light' because the wisdom of the Buddhas eminates radiant light</def>
